### Admin token: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "password": "!@#qweQWE1"
}

### Positive test: Admin can create a new user with correct data
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

{
  "username": "{{$random.uuid}}",
  "password": "{{$random.uuid}}",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with blank username
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "{{$random.uuid}}",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with username 2 or 16 characters
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

{
  "username": "ab",
  "password": "!@#qweQWE1",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with username contains !@#$%^&*(){}[]\|;':"./,<>? characters
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

{
"username": "!@#$%^&*(){}[]|",
"password": "!@#qweQWE1",
"role": "USER"
}

### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with blank password
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

{
  "username": "{{$random.name.lastName}}",
  "password": "   ",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with password without one lower case character
### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with password without digits
### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with password without one upper case character
### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with password without one special character
### Negative test: Admin cannot create a new user with password with spaces

